"Repeat layering process of sponge, coffee syrup and mascarpone mixture to create another layer. Cover glasses with plastic wrap and place into refrigerator for a minimum of 2 hours or overnight to set. Just before serving, dust with extra cocoa powder and decorate with chocolate shavings (optional)."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["100 g almond milk","1 tsp apple cider vinegar","80 g plain flour","½ tsp baking powder","¼ tsp bicarbonate of soda","90 g dairy free margarine","1 pinch salt","80 g caster sugar","¼ tsp vanilla bean paste"]},{"title":"Coffee syrup","content":["200 g brewed espresso coffee","50 g Kahlua®"]},{"title":"Vegan mascarpone","content":["300 g raw cashews","70 g pure maple syrup","120 g coconut oil","1 tsp vanilla bean paste","200 g almond milk"]},{"title":"Assembly","content":["1 - 2 tsp unsweetened cocoa powder, for dusting","30 g dairy free chocolate,  shaved (optional)"]}],"id":"r154191","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-Lb1e63o0pP8\/XZWdeC4-bcI\/AAAAAAAAel8\/V7d-zwlJtyYIcwanc-chpK1y4PxdrrTRACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_HCKckm2C5UxWvW3p.png","title":"Vegan tiramisu","publishedAt":"2017-09-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.6 g","fat":"11.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"23.5 g","calories":"827 kJ \/ 197 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking tray (25 x 17 cm), baking paper, bowl, serving glasses (250 ml), round cookie cutter (5 cm), plastic wrap, oven, freezer, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Dairy free chocolate is often vegan, but always check the label of your products.","You can replace almond milk with soy milk, if preferred."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","3h 20m","6 portions"]}